odulation potential. The implementation of a new quietest\nSun model reduces, by approximately a factor of two, the relative solar forcing\ncompared to the largest previous estimation, while the application of updated\nsolar modulation potential increases the forcing difference between Maunder\nminimum and the present by 25-40 %.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Apr 2018 12:14:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-18"}
